{"title":"南疆之碑——记自卫还击战中牺牲的四五战士","authors":["石祥"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南疆之碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——记自卫还击战中牺牲的四五战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙辰清明节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪洒纪念碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴泪，一巨浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声泣，一霹雷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云遮天白花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪雨化作弹雨飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲恸悼总理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横眉斥魔鬼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军心，不可欺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民心，谁敢违！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镣铐难锁真理在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士赤胆捍丰碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南疆虎狼嚎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越军犯边陲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挪界碑，侵我领土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动刀枪，杀我兄妹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们对他是同志加兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们对我是炸弹加地雷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自卫驱虎豹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还击惩盗匪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士为国捐躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑立南疆边陲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上：槟榔、棕榈、榕树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身边：丁香、罗兰、红梅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑——壮军威。碑——振国威，碑文刻着：中华人民共和国不可侵犯！碑上闪耀着：毛主席、周总理的光辉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年三月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写于河口槟榔寨"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}